    "en": {
      "title": "\"Blue Minister\" is a green flag",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tangalle Nakulogamuwa Railway Station was opened today under the chairmanship of the Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forest Conservation Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera.",
        "The foundation stone for this station was laid by Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera during his tenure as the Minister of Transport.",
        "Mr. Mahinda Amaraweera is also the Senior Vice President of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party and had expressed critical comments in front of the media about the recent amendment of the Constitution of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party.",
        "In the meantime, media reports also appeared that several ministers of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party are going to become members of the United National Party."
      ],
